                  <label-para quote="1" skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">b</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>must not result in amounts owed by an offender being paid in a different order of priority to that set out in <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 105C</citation></changeable> of the Sentencing Act 2002.</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                </para>
              </subprov>
            </amend>
          </para>
          <para>
            <text>Section 83: insert after subsection (1):</text>
            <amend quote="1">
              <subprov skeleton="no">
                <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes" quote="1">1A</label>
                <para>
                  <text>Where a levy is payable under <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 105B</citation></changeable> of the Sentencing Act 2002, an order made under subsection (1) must require payment of the levy at the same time as any other amount payable under the order.</text>
                </para>
